text: Kampong Mungkom (Malay for Mungkom Village) is a village situated in the eastern part of Tutong District, Brunei, within the mukim of Kiudang. The incumbent village head is Mohammad Saiful bin Abdullah Anja, who is also the village head for Kampong Kiudang. It has the postcode TE1743. == References == Mungkom
